channel.description:
[img]https://dl.dropbox.com/u/63711182/Alpha%20pkz%202%20-%20Banner.jpg[/img]
Well I've Been Developing Alpha-Pkz 317 For About 8Weeks And I Got Over 175 Players [Online]
First Ill Talk About the Server And then Ill Put Pictures At the End :D It Was Fun I Fixed Alot of Bugs And Some Dupes That i Found.. Server is Economy But Could Be Pk Base Was : TorvaPkz V1 Added : Nomad - With Hit & Loots SlashBash - Doesnt Hit But i Added Loots Icedemon - Doesnt Hit Either but Drops Elegent Amour..
Fixed Stall For Thieveing You Make About 125m to 99 Thieveing Which Takes Like 30mins
SkillerZone
Need to Fix Fletching [ Laggs u Out] 95% Mining With Good Prices WoodCutting is Okay Could Be Better Fletching Needs to Be Re-Coded RuneCrafting Is Working On 85% of Runes..
DonatorZone
Well The Shops Were Maxed Out With PartyHats And Torva Which Isnt Good For Eco So I Fixed it all And Made one Shop Into Barrows Shop And Other Into Skiller Wear.
I Added Frost Dragons But Never Got to Add Frost Dragon Bones Loot.
Hide Is A Custom Teleport Which Only Owner + Can Do Its Just To Get Away From Everything And Relax :D
NOW FOR THE PICTURES [ ANY QUESTIONS POST IN COMMENTS ]
